<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/27282863">如何将玄幻情节写成硬科幻风格？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3096058" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">看过一些用科学解释西游记的文章，感觉很好玩。人不中二枉少年，求各路大牛回答</div>


</div>
